data.description: Imagine Coming Home To This Newly Renovated 4 Bedroom & 2 Full Bath Expanded Cape With Open Floor Plan In A Mature Tree-Lined Neighborhood With An Abundance Of Natural Light. Features A New Eat-In Kitchen That Includes New Appliances To Make Life Easier and More Efficient All While Helping Lower Your Expenses.  Also Features: New Flooring, The Entire Home Has Been Freshly Painted, Separate Laundry Area, And Ample Closet Space Throughout. This Two-Story Residence Within The Longwood School District Is The Perfect Spot For Your Next Chapter. Featuring Two Spacious Bedrooms On The Main Floor And Two Generous Bedrooms On The 2nd Floor. The Living Room Is Perfect For Spending Quality Time Together And The Dining Area Is Great For Entertaining. Enjoy Afternoons In The Home's Backyard While Entertaining Your Next Summer Gathering. This Home Also Offers A 1 Car Garage, Updated Electric, Newer Windows, Newer Heating System, And Newer Roof.  It's All Here, Ready For You To Move In And Make Your Very Own Memories. Schedule A Showing And Come See What All The Fuss Is About In This One.
